===Child Classes-containers===
The engine child {{wp|data structure}}s are termed containers in Trainz and each defines the parameters and variables the simulator software needs to produce a dynamic working 3D asset.
# {{TR|KD|throttle-power container}}
# {{TR|KD|dynamic-brake container}}
# {{TR|KD|pressure container}}
# {{TR|KD|mass container}}
