===Family Typhaceae===
The '''{{fny-w|Typhaceae}}''' (cattail or bullrush family) naturally contains the genus ''{{fny-w|Typha}}'', which was the sole genus until the {{fny-w|APG III system}} added the genus ''{{fny-w|Sparganium}}'' (bur-reeds) in 2009 by merging the similar family '''Sparganiaceae''' into Typhaceae.

====Subfamily Sparganioideae====
This genus was previously included alone in the family {{fny-w|Sparganiaceae}}.

